Class WordMatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ing.software.ocr.OperativeObjects.WordMatcher

  • public class WordMatcher
extends java.lang.Object
    The scope of this object is to apply the Levenshtein distance algorithm to a subset of regex.

    • Method Detail

      • match

        public double match(OcrText line)
        Get a score of how well the input line matches with the previously passed regex.
        Parameters:
        line - OcrText to match
        Returns:
        value in range [0, maxScore]. maxScore is the value passed in the constructor. 0 means that there was no match.
